{"tid":628404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩日內，金管局四次入市合共買入96.64億港元","createTime":"2018-04-13T22:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T01:08:48.000Z","uid":147314,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"38a6e4725a059c3bff0a16ce5c95b029e16032b0","tid":628404,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T22:06:27.000Z","msg":"金管局再入市買逾33億港元<br />\n<br />\n2018-04-14 HKT 05:23<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1391113_1_20180414052438.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1391113_1_20180414052438.jpg&h=dcdfaa81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金管局再度入市承接港元沽盤，買入33.68億港元，以維持港元匯價穩定。（shutterstock）<br />\n<br />\n港元持續疲弱，多次觸發7.85弱方兌換保證，在本港清晨時間，金管局再度入市承接港元沽盤，買入33.68億港元，以維持港元匯價穩定。兩日內，金管局四次入市合共買入96.64億港元，下星期二銀行體系結餘減少至大約1701億港元。<br />\n<br />\n金管局入市後，港元匯價維持在7.85港元兌1美元水平上落。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391113-20180414.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391113-20180414.htm&d=W7b%2BWNj1u%2BV7aCy48ljdW10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=d9b8860d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1391113-20180414.htm&h=04f893ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1391113-20180414.htm</a>"},{"pid":"bd142fdad77260e778fe056ba10231cfa9473759","tid":628404,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T22:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a963a3871520e1632830a18f68234242fd1fc26","tid":628404,"uid":28523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T22:25:57.000Z","msg":"其實有咩分法可以解決？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 唔識"},{"pid":"1b787b08c0aef306d336d34960c0599faae67557","tid":628404,"uid":28523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot